{"tid":1590353,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣國際戰］用新hashtag #SaveHongKongersSaveTheWorld","createTime":"2019-09-23T16:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T16:25:05.000Z","uid":276987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a5e513bd95c97c0e1679c3100f15cf6ce702cd50","tid":1590353,"uid":276987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:23:35.000Z","msg":"我哋而家文宣國際戰，重點側重中共、政府、黑警違反人權、用殘暴手段打壓香港人，希望令西方國家睇唔過眼，用行動支持香港。你諗返以前見到中共打壓法輪功、新疆、西藏，都令人睇唔過眼，但人類都係會自私既，唔係殺到埋身嘅問題，都係得閒先會幫口講兩句，見你還手又話你撐唔落，跟住就索性唔理。<br />\n<br />\n所以我提議加一個新tagline俾文宣用: <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Save the HongKongers, save the world</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n#SaveHongKongersSaveTheWorld</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n令外國人容易意識到中共壯大會威脅文明社會嘅普世價值，而家世界就處於十字路口，要救香港以滅中共，就好像Heroes入面要在此刻拯救cheerleader，未來世界才能避過浩劫。咁樣外國人先會覺得我地嘅問題影響到佢地，先會關注同用實際行動撐香港人。"},{"pid":"3d8eb8a4590b25753708672dfefb7a43aeefec9f","tid":1590353,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"}]}